{"tid":1038413,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"好戲講得多,好既導演又點睇??","createTime":"2019-02-26T15:58:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-27T14:58:46.000Z","uid":12720,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"f4c4198ae4776645ffc9e7f964a5e8949dc47dbd","tid":1038413,"uid":12720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T15:58:08.000Z","msg":"成日講三寶就講得多啦~好小有人討論下導演<br />\n以下排名不分先後,只係小弟既喜愛<br />\nSteven Spielberg : 全能 ,記錄 劇情 科幻 特技 改編等...所有類型都可拿捏 大量經典電影<br />\nChristopher Nolan : 10套全部佳作 ,商業片王, 熱愛IMAX<br />\nDavid Fincher : Se7en ,Gone Girl ,Fight Club等 劇情懸疑片...<br />\nJames Cameron : 票房神話 , 真3D帶領者 , Alita之父- Avatar ,Aliens ,Terminator ,Titanic 等經典 <br />\nPeter Jackson : King Kong ,魔介/哈比人 系列等 史詩長片<br />\nGeorge Miller : Mad Max系列<br />\nRon Howard : Beautiful Mind , Rush, Da Vinci Code , Angels &amp; Demons 亦主要係我鐘意湯漢斯<br />\nMatthew Vaughn : Kick-Ass ,First Class , Kingsman<br />\nMartin Scorsese : Shutter Island.無間道風雲,華爾街狼人<br />\nPaul Greengrass : Captain Phillips , Jason Bourne 等動作系列<br />\n<br />\n大家又覺得邊位最全能,對電影最有貢獻?<br />\n等大家補充同推介好片~~~"},{"pid":"2974cde17ae3c68d5887e352562d693a8512889e","tid":1038413,"uid":10062,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T17:10:19.000Z","msg":"都係例牌嗰啲<br />\n黑澤明<br />\n小津安二郎<br />\n寇比力克<br />\n高達<br />\n岩井俊二<br />\n杜琪峰<br />\n王家衛"},{"pid":"9423c3ad8fd7cabeb51148f67604cbaad5a93a38","tid":1038413,"uid":89030,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T17:15:06.000Z","msg":"Damien, Chazelle: Whiplash, La La Land, First Man<br />\nDenis Villeneuve: Prisoners, Sicario, Arrival, Blade Runner 2049<br />\nWes Anderson: Grand Budapest Hotel, Isle of Dogs"},{"pid":"c923d52501bc6b127f25bf6463736b045a358d3d","tid":1038413,"uid":84205,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T17:17:12.000Z","msg":"Quentin Tarantino: Pulp Fiction, Inglourious Basterds, Django Unchained"},{"pid":"619c0ae8a2f7db65836ec37c3714b467217fb23b","tid":1038413,"uid":70800,"